sections.data_availability:
Majority of the datasets utilized are publicly available at the NASA GeneLab website (
https://osdr.nasa.gov/bio/repo
), including rodent data; Adrenal glands (OSD-98), Extensor digitorum longus muscle (OSD-99), Eye (OSD-100), Gastrocnemius muscle (OSD-101), Kidney (OSD-102), Quadriceps Muscle (OSD-103), Soleus muscle (OSD-104), Tibialis anterior muscle (OSD-105), Liver (OSD-168, OSD-48), Skin (OSD-238, OSD-239, OSD-240, OSD-241, OSD-254), JAXA CFE data (OSD-530).

